data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED*Assumable loan option with a low 3.1% interest rate* Discover the perfect Florida retreat in the serene community of Jasmine Trails! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a haven of comfort and convenience for any family. The master suite boasts a huge walk-in closet, a luxurious bathroom with granite countertops, double showers, and sinks for your ultimate relaxation. The kitchen is a culinary dream with ample wood cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a very large double door pantry and even a coffee bar! But that's not all – there's a bonus space for an office or extra family room. You'll find ample storage in the 2-car garage and a shed in the completely fenced in private backyard. Enjoy the community pool and clubhouse just a short walk away. The HOA fee is a mere $47 a month and covers all community amenities! You can even book the clubhouse for special occasions and take advantage of the shuffleboard court! If you're a traveler or own a travel trailer, this home offers fenced-in storage for your convenience. Plus, it's strategically located between two of the top US beaches and the beautiful Florida springs. Explore Buccaneer Bay Weeki Wachee Spring Park, just 30 minutes away, where you can cool off in crystal-clear spring waters and witness captivating mermaid shows.  For dining with a view, "Sam's on the Beach" is a 4.5-star restaurant where you can savor seafood and more while gazing at the ocean and enjoying live music. Hudson Beach is just 10 minutes away, perfect for launching your boat.  This friendly and peaceful neighborhood maintains its charm thanks to the HOA. Recent upgrades, like new French doors, ensure a comfortable living space with a roof inspection guaranteeing worry-free living for years to come. Buyer to verify room measurements.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful Florida home yours. Call today and start living the Florida dream!
